                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>San Francisco</placeName>\n                <date>May 18. 1857</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">I have duly<lb/> received yours of the <date>19<hi rend=\"sup\"\n                        >th</hi> February</date>, &amp; I hope<lb/> you will excuse me for not\n                writing to you<lb/> ere this, as I have been continually closely<lb/> occupied for\n                the last few months.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">In the <date>20<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> of April</date>, I have sent\n                you by letter to <persName>Mr. M. Roggenburger</persName> a Dft. Of 33—,<lb/> which\n                I trust you have recd in the full en-<lb/>joyment of health.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I send you enclosed a statement of<lb/> your a/c, which exhibits\n                Balance of 13.42 on<lb/> hand, which I shall endeavor to swell to<lb/> a larger\n                amt., &amp; then I'll remit. In the said<lb/> statement you will perceive what is\n                for the<lb/> “Occident” &amp; acknowledge the same as usual<lb/> in the “Occ.” I\n                have settled with <persName>Haas</persName><lb/> &amp;\n                    <persName>Rosenfeld</persName> for $97 to be in <hi rend=\"underline\">full</hi>\n                &amp; they<lb/> desire a discontinuance of the subscription<lb/> of the O. that in\n                the best I could effect<lb/> with them. <persName>Mr. S. R. Rosenthal</persName>\n                also wishes<lb/> to discontinue the “Occid.,” &amp; promised to pay<lb/> son his\n                subscription dues. <persName>Mr. Dessau</persName> has<lb/> left the state with his\n                family, &amp; I do not see<lb/> any chance how you will ever receive<lb/> one Cent\n                from him. I hope you have</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p39s1m54q/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
