          "annotations": [
            {
              "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p39s1m54q/canvas/p3/annopage",
              "type": "AnnotationPage",
              "items": [
                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p39s1m54q/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>I regret very much that the writings should<lb/> trouble you so much. You should\n                remember,<lb/> that the mass of the people are capable<lb/> of judging between right\n                &amp; wrong, &amp; there-<lb/>fore your severe opponents cannot hurt<lb/> you. As a\n                journalist you must expect<lb/> such attacks, &amp; your success in meeting<lb/>\n                them reflects upon your credit &amp; honor.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I have with much gratification learned<lb/> that you are being\n                elected as minister of<lb/> a new Portuguese congregation in\n                    <placeName>Phil.</placeName>;<lb/> allow me to extend my congratulations,\n                &amp;<lb/> my sincere wishes for true success.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The news relating to Jewish affairs are<lb/> very dull &amp; scarce.\n                The congregation<lb/> Emanu-El, are now without any<lb/> minister; they are\n                anxiously awaiting<lb/> a response of some suitable person to their advertisements.\n                An able man can<lb/> here find a good post, &amp; can find a<lb/> wide field for\n                doing good. The congre-<lb/>gation at their last meeting have changed<lb/> the\n                resolution effecting the election of<lb/> a minister, so that $3000— salary\n                annually<lb/> is paid for 2 years &amp;c. I understand<lb/> that you have officially\n                been informed of this<lb/> change, &amp; that an advertisement to that effect<lb/>\n                had been ordered. <persName>Mr. D. Levy</persName> is now<lb/> the teacher of the\n                Hebrew School attached</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p39s1m54q/canvas/p3"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
